      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Advanced Class Guide pg. 209</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 5th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Price</strong> +4,000 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>Burdenless armor distributes the weight of the wearer's load more efficiently, allowing her to carry more without suffering the effects of encumbrance. The wearer's carrying capacity is increased by 50% across each load (light, medium and heavy).</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>effortless armor</em><sup>UC</sup>; <strong>Price</strong> 2,000 gp</p>",
